"file_path":"/qyVl3aPgxxTHqyfXMWeCcryPR30.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/ArpD3Imbvj4diy0AH5LwNK7fxuy.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":0},{"width":2048,"height":1152,"file_path":"/3IMMedngi2CtOIrM7Ahk8LS1aqy.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/7hZIkjjjhTLVTXG8zyrwNGkHrXF.jpg","iso_639_1":"he","vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/qG2pxw5bQpSUiSYODxPTOUZ7oX4.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/8giNgctbqCxGQYHtIIngFz4pxS.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-21T10:22:14.064+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":106,"tagline":"Sometimes there really are monsters under your bed.","homepage":"https://www.dustbunnyfilm.com/","overview":"Ten-year-old Aurora asks her hitman neighbor to kill the monster under her bed that she claims ate her family. To protect her, he must battle an onslaught of assassins while accepting that some monsters are real."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Toz Yumağı","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Atrapando a un monstruo","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Una niña de ocho años le pide ayuda a su insidiosa vecina en su misión para matar al monstruo que vive debajo de su cama, el cual, según ella, devoró a su familia."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"더스트 바니","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"“어른도 아이도 함께하는 몬스터 사냥 이야기”  열 살 소녀 오로라는 침대 밑에 숨어 있다고 믿는 정체불명의 괴물 때문에 자신의 가족이 사라졌다고 믿는다. 아무도 그녀의 말을 믿어주지 않자, 오로라는 복도를 사이에 둔 신비로운 이웃 - 몬스터 -를 사냥하는 것으로 보이는 청부살인업자에게 도움을 청한다. 그는 처음엔 의심하면서도 그녀의 부탁을 받아들이고, 두 사람은 함께 진짜 괴물과 맞서며 이들이 마주한 위험한 세상과 서로의 상처를 이해해 가게 되는데…"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"Parfois, il y a vraiment des monstres sous votre lit.","homepage":"","overview":"Aurora, dix ans, demande à un tueur à gages d'éliminer le monstre qui, selon elle, a dévoré toute sa famille. Pour la protéger, il devra affronter une horde d'assassins tout en acceptant l'idée que certains monstres existent bel et bien."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"O Monstro do Meu Quarto","runtime":106,"tagline":"Às vezes, realmente existem monstros debaixo da sua cama.","homepage":"","overview":"Aurora, uma menina de 10 anos, tem um vizinho misterioso que mata monstros da vida real. Ele é um assassino de aluguel. Então, quando Aurora precisa de ajuda para matar o monstro que ela acredita ter devorado toda a sua família, ela contrata os serviços dele. Suspeitando que seus pais possam ter sido vítimas de assassinos que o perseguiam, o vizinho de Aurora aceita o trabalho, sentindo-se culpado. Agora, para protegê-la, ele precisará lutar contra uma horda de assassinos — e aceitar que alguns monstros são reais."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Atrapando A Un Monstruo","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Una niña de ocho años pide ayuda a su intrigante vecino para matar al monstruo que hay debajo de su cama y que cree que se comió a su familia."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":106,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ein zehnjähriges Mädchen verbündet sich mit ihrem Nachbarn, um sich gemeinsam ihren inneren und äußeren Monstern zu stellen. Aurora ist überzeugt: Ein Monster hat ihre Familie verschlungen. Ihre letzte Hoffnung ruht auf dem unheimlichen Mann von nebenan – von dem es heißt, er töte „echte“ Monster. In Wahrheit ist er ein abgebrühter Auftragsmörder.  Was als skurrile Geschichte beginnt, entwickelt sich rasch zu einem düsteren Geflecht aus Gewalt, Schuld und kindlicher Vorstellungskraft. Realität und Illusion verschwimmen – und am Ende bleibt die Frage: Wer sind die wahren Monster? Eine fesselnde Reise in die dunklen Winkel der Fantasie, ein gnadenloser Rachefeldzug – voller schwarzem Humor, bizarrer Kreaturen und brutaler Konsequenzen. Ein düsteres Märchen voller Vorstellungskraft, Witz -und einem ganz besonderen Monsterhasen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"أرنب الغبار","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"تدور الأحداث في إطار من التشويق حول فتاة تبلغ من العمر ثمان سنوات تعتقد أن هناك وحش تحت سريرها تسبب في موت عائلتها، لذا تطلب المساعدة من جارتهم الماكرة."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Поймать монстра","runtime":106,"tagline":"«Иногда под кроватью действительно прячутся монстры»","homepage":"","overview":"Десятилетняя Аврора нанимает своего таинственного соседа, чтобы тот уничтожил монстра, поглотившего её семью. Подозревая, что родители девочки могли пасть жертвой киллеров, охотящихся на него самого, мужчина с чувством вины берётся за дело."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Монстр під ліжком","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"8-річна дівчинка просить свого сусіда, найманого вбивцю, позбутися монстра, що ховається під ліжком і, як вона думає, з’їв її батьків. Кілер береться до справи й стає на захист своєї юної замовниці, тепер він бореться не лише із уявними, а й з реальними монстрами."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Čudovište ispod kreveta","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Desetogodišnja djevojčica Aurora je uvjerena da ispod njezina kreveta vreba čudovište – i ima dobar razlog za strah: upravo je pojelo njezine udomitelje. Njeno rješenje je neobično, ali praktično: unajmit će enigmatičnog susjeda, plaćenog ubojicu, da se obračuna s nemani. No susjed vjeruje kako su njezini roditelji zapravo stradali od metaka namijenjenih njemu, pa njihovo neočekivano savezništvo prerasta u jezivu, ali i dirljivu priču."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"邦尼殺死他","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"小女孩奧蘿拉深信，她家中的地板下，潛伏著一隻吃掉她全家的神秘怪物。孤身一人的她，決定向隔壁冷峻的鄰居求助，因為她發現這位看似平凡的男人竟是一名職業殺手！奧蘿拉鼓起勇氣、設法籌到一筆錢，決定「雇用」這位殺手對付怪物。然而，殺手很快意識到，這隻「怪物」可能並非虛構，而是潛伏在他周圍、試圖追殺自己的刺客。為了保護奧蘿拉，他不得不迎擊接二連三的致命襲擊，同時向神秘女子探查真相。隨著危機逼近，兩人的命運緊密交織，而奧蘿拉口中的「怪物」，竟可能比任何人想像得更真實、更可怕…。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"尘兔","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"小女孩奥萝拉深信，家中的地板下潜伏着一只吃掉她全家的神秘怪物。 她决定向隔壁冷峻的邻居求助，因为她发现这位看似平凡的男人竟是一名职业杀手！"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Prachová příšera","runtime":0,"tagline":"Někdy se pod postelí opravdu skrývají příšery.","homepage":"","overview":"Po náhlém zmizení své rodiny zůstává osmiletá Aurora sama ve velkém, tichém domě. Věří, že za vším stojí děsivá příšera ukrytá pod její postelí – příšera, která se živí těmi, které miluje. Zoufalá a vyděšená se obrátí na jediného člověka, kterému se odváží svěřit: svého souseda (Mads Mikkelsen). Ten je však známý spíš svými pochybnými plány než dobrosrdečností. Společně se pouštějí do bizarního a nebezpečného plánu na zničení stvůry. Čím hlouběji se noří do temných koutů domu – i svých vlastních myslí – tím nejasnější je, co je skutečné a co jen plodem dětského strachu… nebo dospělé zvrácenosti. Hra na hrdiny se mění v děsivý boj o přežití, kde může každý krok vést k odhalení děsivé pravdy. Dust Bunny je napínavý a znepokojivý příběh o dětské nevinnosti, zlu, které číhá ve stínech, a hranici mezi fantazií a šílenstvím. (Vertical Entertainment)"},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Porszörny","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A tízéves Aurora mellett egy titokzatos férfi él, aki valódi szörnyekre vadászik – hivatásos gyilkos. Amikor a kislánynak szüksége lesz valakire, aki megszabadítja őt a családját elpusztító szörnytől, a férfi segítségét kéri. A vadász azonban úgy sejti, hogy Aurora szüleit valójában azok a bérgyilkosok ölték meg, akik eredetileg őt akarták eltenni láb alól, ezért lelkiismereti okokból elfogadja a megbízást. Hogy megóvja Aurorát, egész sereg merénylővel kell szembenéznie – és közben rá kell döbbennie, hogy némelyik szörny igenis létezik.  (Csillag Lajos)R3"},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"מפלצות אמיתיות","runtime":0,"tagline":"לפעמים באמת יש מפלצות מתחת למיטה שלך.","homepage":"","overview":"השכן המסתורי של אורורה בת ה-10 הוא מתנקש להשכרה, אז כשאורורה צריכה עזרה להרוג את המפלצת שמסתתרת מתחת למיטתה, ושהיא מאמינה שטרפה את הוריה החורגים, היא שוכרת את שירותיו. השכן, שחושד שהוריה נפלו קורבן למתנקשים שחיפשו אותו, לוקח את העבודה מתוך אשמה. כדי להגן על אורורה, הוא יצטרך להילחם בשורה של מתנקשים, ולקבל את העובדה שלפעמים, מפלצות הן אמיתיות."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"怪奇魔塵事件","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"十歲女孩奧蘿拉深信，床下的怪物已吞噬她的家人。孤立無援下，她決定僱用神秘鄰居——一個正被追殺的職業殺手（麥斯米基辛 飾），替她「解決」那隻怪物。殺手自身難保，卻接下這單來自孩子的委託。當冷血專業撞上童真執念，兩人結成最不可能同盟。  面對的床底下黑影，究竟是一場女孩的幻想遊戲，還是大人們不敢直視的現實？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Putekļu monstrs","runtime":106,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Astoņus gadus veca meitene lūdz savu viltīgo kaimiņu palīdzēt nogalināt monstru zem viņas gultas, kurš, kā viņa domā, ir apēdis viņas ģimeni."},"name":"Latviešu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"},{"data":{"title":"Quái Vật Dưới Gầm Giường","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Một sát thủ bảo vệ cô bé tin rằng gia đình mình bị quái vật giết hại, và dần nhận ra những nỗi sợ trẻ con có thể là sự thật."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":106,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"De tienjarige Aurora vraagt ​​haar buurman, een huurmoordenaar, om het monster te doden waarvan ze gelooft dat het haar hele familie heeft opgegeten. Om haar te beschermen, moet hij een horde huurmoordenaars verslaan en tegelijkertijd accepteren dat sommige monsters echt bestaan."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Aurora, una bambina di dieci anni, chiede al suo vicino sicario di uccidere il mostro sotto il suo letto che, secondo lei, ha divorato la sua famiglia. Per proteggerla, il vicino deve affrontare un'ondata di assassini, accettando al contempo che alcuni mostri siano reali."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"เผยตัวอย่างแรกออกมาแล้ว  Dust Bunny  หนัง Dark Fantasy กำกับโดย Bryan Fuller ผู้สร้าง Hannibal นำแสดงโดย Mads Mikkelsen  ,David Dastmalchian  Sigourney Weaver และ Sophie Sloan\r เล่าเรื่องของเด็กหญิงวัย 8 ขวบที่ไปขอให้เพื่อนบ้านที่ไม่น่าไว้วางใจของเธอให้มาช่วยกำจัดสัตว์ประหลาดที่อยู่ใจใต้เตียงที่เธอคิดว่ามันกินครอบครัวของเธอไป"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":106,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Den tiårige Aurora beder sin nabo, der er lejemorder, om at dræbe det monster under hendes seng, som hun påstår har spist hendes familie. For at beskytte hende må han kæmpe mod et angreb af snigmordere, samtidig med at han accepterer, at nogle monstre findes."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Monstrul din camera mea","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"O fetiță de 10 ani face echipă cu un asasin profesionist pentru a-și înfrunta demonii cu care se confruntă fiecare dintre ei. Micuța Aurora are un vecin misterios care ucide monștri reali, ca meserie; este asasin plătit. Aurora îl angajează atunci când are nevoie să îl distrugă pe monstrul din camera ei care se pare că i-a mâncat toată familia. Reticent, dar sensibilizat, vecinul asasin devine protectorul ei împotriva criminalilor periculoși și a monștrilor care se dovedesc a fi reali."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Kraina Mroku","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ośmioletnia dziewczynka prosi tajemniczego sąsiada o pomoc w zgładzeniu potwora żyjącego pod jej łóżkiem, którego podejrzewa o pożarcie jej rodziny."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En hitman tar på sig uppdraget att hjälpa sin åttaåriga granne att hitta de monster som hon tror har rövat bort hennes föräldrar, ett uppdrag han accepterar då han misstänker att föräldrarna i själva verket mördats av någon som är ute efter honom själv."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Прашният заек","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Десетгодишната Аврора моли съседа си – наемен убиец – да премахне чудовището под леглото ѝ, за което твърди, че е погълнало семейството ѝ. За да я защити, той трябва да се справи с натиска от други убийци и да приеме, че понякога чудовищата са истински."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"10-letna Aurora prosi svojega soseda, poklicnega morilca, naj ubije pošast pod njeno posteljo, za katero trdi, da je pojedla njeno družino. Da bi jo zaščitil, se mora spopasti z naletom morilcev, hkrati pa sprejeti dejstvo, da so nekatere pošasti tudi resnične."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ενα 10χρονο κορίτσι, το οποίο ενώνει τις δυνάμεις του με τον εκτελεστή γείτονά της, ο οποίος σκοτώνει πραγματικά τέρατα επί πληρωμή. Έτσι, όταν η Aurora χρειάζεται βοήθεια για να σκοτώσει το τέρας που πιστεύει ότι έφαγε ολόκληρη την οικογένειά της, ζητά τις υπηρεσίες του. Υποψιασμένος ότι οι γονείς της Aurora μπορεί να έχουν πέσει θύματα δολοφόνων που τον κυνηγούν, ο γείτονας αναλαμβάνει με ενοχές τη δουλειά."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ti år gamle Aurora ber naboen sin, som er leiemorder, om å drepe monsteret under sengen som hun påstår har spist familien hennes. For å beskytte henne må han kjempe mot en bølge av snikmordere, samtidig som han må innse at enkelte monstre faktisk eksisterer."},"name":"Bokmål","iso_639_1":"nb","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian Bokmål"},{"data":{"title":"خرگوش پشمالو","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"داستان اورورا، دختری ده‌ساله با ذهنی پر از ترس و کابوس که پس از یک حادثه تلخ مطمئن می‌شود هیولایی در زیر تختش پنهان است و خانواده‌اش را بلعیده. او برای نابودی این موجود به همسایه مرموزش، که گذشته‌ای تاریک و خطرناک دارد، پناه می‌برد. اما هرچه جلوتر می‌رود، درمی‌یابد مرز میان خیال و واقعیت از همیشه باریک‌تر است…"},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Prachová príšera","runtime":0,"tagline":"Niekedy sú naozaj pod posteľou príšery.","homepage":"","overview":"Po náhlom zmiznutí svojej rodiny zostáva osemročná Aurora sama vo veľkom, tichom dome. Verí, že za všetkým stojí desivá príšera ukrytá pod jej posteľou – príšera, ktorá sa živí tými, ktorých miluje. Zúfalá a vydesená sa obráti na jediného človeka, ktorému sa odváži zveriť: svojho suseda (Mads Mikkelsen). Ten je však známy skôr svojimi pochybnými plánmi než dobrosrdečnosťou. Spoločne sa púšťajú do bizarného a nebezpečného plánu na zničenie stvory. Čím hlbšie sa ponárajú do temných kútov domu – aj svojich vlastných myslí – tým nejasnejšie je, čo je skutočné a čo len plodom detského strachu… alebo dospelej zvrátenosti. Hra na hrdinov sa mení na desivý boj o prežitie, kde môže každý krok viesť k odhaleniu desivej pravdy. Dust Bunny je napínavý a znepokojivý príbeh o detskej nevinnosti, zle, ktoré číha v tieňoch, a hranici medzi fantáziou a šialenstvom."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"Tamsos zuikis","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dešimties metų Aurora turi paslaptingą kaimyną, kuris žudo tikrus monstrus – jis yra samdomas žudikas. Kai Aurorai prireikia pagalbos nužudyti monstrą, kuris, jos manymu, suėdė visą jos šeimą, ji kreipiasi į jį dėl paslaugų. Įtardamas, kad Auroros tėvai galėjo tapti ją medžiojančių žudikų aukomis, kaimynas priima šį darbą. Norėdamas apsaugoti mergaitę, jis turės atremti atakas ir pripažinti, kad kai kurie monstrai yra tikri."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"6939b7e6f77121dd10dfa5e2","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/6939b7e6f77121dd10dfa5e2","author":"Manuel São Bento","content":"FULL SPOILER-FREE REVIEW @ https://movieswetextedabout.com/dust-bunny-movie-review-mads-mikkelsen-and-sophie-sloan-elevate-a-familiar-tale/\r\n\r\n\"Dust Bunny doesn't reinvent the wheel or say something profoundly new about grief and trauma, but it manages to be a satisfying experience. It's a \"silly\" film in its conception, and its VFX might not dazzle, but it's all executed with evident affection and clarity of purpose.\r\n\r\nThere's a positive and clear message about sensitive matters, wrapped in a somewhat humorous and innocent layer that, with the due warning about \"accessible violence\", can be appreciated by various ages.\r\n\r\nBryan Fuller reminds us that the monsters under the bed are as real as the pain that feeds them, and that true courage lies not in having no fear, but in finding someone who believes in our truth enough to help us turn on the light.\"\r\n\r\nRating: B-","created_at":"2025-12-10T18:11:50.687Z","updated_at":"2025-12-10T18:11:50.716Z","author_details":{"name":"Manuel São Bento","rating":6,"username":"msbreviews","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":1241983,"adult":false,"title":"Train Dreams","video":false,"overview":"A logger leads a life of quiet grace as he experiences love and loss during an era of monumental change in early 20th-century America.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.4903,"vote_count":714,"poster_path":"/wfzYOVdafdbD1d3SxNqiBtV2Yhx.jpg","release_date":"2025-11-05","vote_average":7.336,"backdrop_path":"/gwohbraLtlTW7F9EAyxOckSBwf3.jpg","original_title":"Train Dreams","original_language":"en"},{"id":125521,"adult":false,"title":"Slayers Return","video":false,"overview":"Lina Inverse and Naga the White Serpent are back! What begins as a routine bandit-stomping turns into the adventure of a lifetime involving magical golems, an ancient Elven weapon and even someone bent on destroying the world. It's a predicament only Lina and Naga could get themselves in to.","genre_ids":[16,12,35,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1817,"vote_count":2073,"poster_path":"/fNQx9YD4nxpcWvriVm1paIxbMwB.jpg","release_date":"1996-08-03","vote_average":6.546,"backdrop_path":"/1SeydkGlChbUrYJeV95TNSLQsFt.jpg","original_title":"スレイヤーズ RETURN","original_language":"ja"},{"id":16690,"adult":false,"title":"Return to Never Land","video":false,"overview":"In 1940, the world is besieged by World War II. Wendy, all grown up, has two children; including Jane, who does not believe Wendy's stories about Peter Pan.","genre_ids":[12,14,16,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.6632,"vote_count":2378,"poster_path":"/wB3r2b8sxUZspqNyr8copMlt7se.jpg","release_date":"2002-02-14","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/tz0MjeUUGgyfNfBPiIksaqEgos6.jpg","original_title":"Return to Never Land","original_language":"en"},{"id":359983,"adult":false,"title":"The Lion Guard: Return of the Roar","video":false,"overview":"Set in the African savannah, the film follows Kion as he assembles the members of the 'Lion Guard'. Throughout the film, the diverse team of young animals will learn how to utilize each of their unique abilities to solve problems and accomplish tasks to maintain balance within the Circle of Life, while also introducing viewers to the vast array of animals that populate the prodigious African landscape.","genre_ids":[10751,10770,16,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2598,"vote_count":1219,"poster_path":"/pzcQ7cQBHIdsKLN4exd7bCyy1pk.jpg","release_date":"2016-01-25","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/sYbdAWcTqcdLtpAnwIWjrIw6t0r.jpg","original_title":"The Lion Guard: Return of the Roar","original_language":"en"},{"id":437544,"adult":false,"title":"People","video":false,"overview":"Six vignettes pit an assortment of characters against each other in everyday situations.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8287,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/tXKAlTxGsiMkmomgXouIUU26gmt.jpg","release_date":"2016-04-22","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/e125vbf6UsyfwYU3tlAAKu8D9jx.jpg","original_title":"People","original_language":"en"},{"id":689761,"adult":false,"title":"People","video":false,"overview":"The Red Mountain Tribe hangs out in my backyard. \"Lipton's lovely home movie PEOPLE, in its affection for valuable inconsequential gestures, indicates in the course of its three minutes why there has to be a continuing alternative to the commercial cinema.\" – Roger Greenspun, The New York Times","genre_ids":[],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1189,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/qAOHtIsc92U62FZytpCNssZlHLF.jpg","release_date":"1969-04-02","vote_average":8.3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"People","original_language":"en"},{"id":19142,"adult":false,"title":"The Return of Swamp Thing","video":false,"overview":"The Swamp Thing returns to battle the evil Dr. Arcane, who has a new science lab full of creatures transformed by genetic mutation, and chooses Heather Locklear as his new object of affection.","genre_ids":[27,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0442,"vote_count":257,"poster_path":"/5sm1Yi1hgj805b9o2a1uC6BXhqw.jpg","release_date":"1989-05-11","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/vTGbFAFh3cGAFeLaXS8M3l3sl9z.jpg","original_title":"The Return of Swamp Thing","original_language":"en"},{"id":72032,"adult":false,"title":"Return of Sabata","video":false,"overview":"Master gunslinger Sabata arrives in Hobsonville, a town completely owned by McIntock, a robber baron who is taxing the inhabitants for the cost of future improvements to the town. Or that's what McIntock says he'll do with the money...","genre_ids":[37],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6211,"vote_count":155,"poster_path":"/dI2IU9a69lk7DwJ2aAsbDoNOfuX.jpg","release_date":"1971-09-03","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/v4fn0Bho1aMNLCNfaGuqXrXCZwq.jpg","original_title":"È tornato Sabata... hai chiuso un'altra volta!","original_language":"it"},{"id":803329,"adult":false,"title":".hack//G.U. Returner","video":false,"overview":"The characters receive an email from Ovan requesting them to go to Δ Hidden Forbidden Festival where a mysterious summer festival is set up. There they encounter an AIDA Chim Chim who wishes to peacefully co-exist with the players of The World. It then transforms into the word \"Returner\", which Haseo assumes it to mean that Ovan will return to The World.","genre_ids":[18,10770,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4702,"vote_count":43,"poster_path":"/hQ9H4dee9NKHT3sHHA4Dc336Bwe.jpg","release_date":"2007-01-18","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/7v8GvuUmAmxMqpODPHYs6keK7Fp.jpg","original_title":".hack//G.U. Returner","original_language":"ja"},{"id":28260,"adult":false,"title":"Return of the Living Dead III","video":false,"overview":"Having recently witnessed the horrific results of a top secret project to bring the dead back to life, a distraught teenager performs the operation on his girlfriend after she's killed in a motorcycle accident.","genre_ids":[27,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.38,"vote_count":894,"poster_path":"/lu4Eit7pR5I8hGHJmy3K9Re8FPo.jpg","release_date":"1993-10-01","vote_average":6.567,"backdrop_path":"/3eYQyFx4QQ5j0L0wqjEoC8I1RvF.jpg","original_title":"Return of the Living Dead III","original_language":"en"},{"id":42436,"adult":false,"title":"Natale in crociera","video":false,"overview":"Paolo Cioffa, as Christmas approaches, is ready to leave on a cruise with his mistress Magda Venni, freed by his wife Francesca Zanchi and his son Federico, who is about to go skiing.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.382,"vote_count":422,"poster_path":"/n83LsfQCPReYembtNtuGwqUkUOS.jpg","release_date":"2007-12-14","vote_average":4.948,"backdrop_path":"/iweTLbiGNv42fNcgQTmg19n0s0T.jpg","original_title":"Natale in crociera","original_language":"it"},{"id":1133564,"adult":false,"title":"Rewind 3: The Final Chapter","video":false,"overview":"An unfortunate highschooler finds an ancient book that summons Allentown's deadliest maniacs back from the dead.","genre_ids":[27,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1208,"vote_count":12,"poster_path":"/dkA7kdMnpYH4qHOtmLqLCBfn7Cs.jpg","release_date":"2023-08-17","vote_average":5.333,"backdrop_path":"/3RvmiJTzarRJQDKfIqBHMDtzY1y.jpg","original_title":"Rewind 3: The Final Chapter","original_language":"en"},{"id":99704,"adult":false,"title":"WWE WrestleMania XXVIII","video":true,"overview":"The Rock and John Cena collide in the most anticipated WrestleMania face-off in history, an epic match that will forever define the legacies of these icons. The Deadman stakes his entire legacy on one battle with Triple H inside the nightmarish prison they immortalized, Hell In A Cell, with The Heartbreak Kid Shawn Michaels as special guest referee. WWE Champion CM Punk faces off against Chris Jericho in the explosive clash of revolutionaries that will determine which man truly is “The Best In The World.” Daniel Bryan defends his title against a riled-up and ruthless Sheamus, who will have to fight through The Submission Specialist’s tactics to claim his first World Heavyweight Championship. Team Teddy takes on Team Johnny to determine which man will win total control of Raw and SmackDown.  This was the twenty-eighth annual WrestleMania. It took place on April 1, 2012 at Sun Life Stadium in Miami Gardens, Florida. It is the highest grossing PPV event in professional wrestling history.","genre_ids":[28,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7803,"vote_count":95,"poster_path":"/nvjIVVBQR6vo17FBl3AHGc4jtsc.jpg","release_date":"2012-04-01","vote_average":7.916,"backdrop_path":"/svzSyqWX7TnyN7f4OS7krzt3nb5.jpg","original_title":"WWE WrestleMania XXVIII","original_language":"en"},{"id":1091834,"adult":false,"title":"Return","video":false,"overview":"RETURN tells the story of a retired Green Beret who embarks on a healing journey from Montana to Vietnam. There he retraces his steps, shares his wartime experiences with his son, treats his Post-Traumatic Stress Disorder, and seeks out the mountain tribespeople he once lived with and fought alongside as a Special Forces officer.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3396,"vote_count":408,"poster_path":"/opYp1lkbVHVJil8N0c5HRSB5D96.jpg","release_date":"2023-02-19","vote_average":6.793,"backdrop_path":"/8qgqVW4vW2fzodscB28cnNhOzwU.jpg","original_title":"Return","original_language":"en"},{"id":49573,"adult":false,"title":"Flower & Snake","video":false,"overview":"Shizuka is the aristocratic wife of the president of a large company. When she wants to divorce her domineering husband, he orders his employee Yoshi, the son of an adult toy store owner, to train his wife to become sexually submissive.","genre_ids":[53,18,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6206,"vote_count":48,"poster_path":"/n3vMxxuEBylPe3uWAo87qvlcry6.jpg","release_date":"1974-06-22","vote_average":5.4,"backdrop_path":"/5a0SIrDJKRdVD9CLXf9wsyGeF1j.jpg","original_title":"花と蛇","original_language":"ja"},{"id":207680,"adult":false,"title":"Return to... Return to Nuke 'Em High aka Vol. 2","video":false,"overview":"Following the events of Volume 1,  the mutated glee club continue their violent rampage in Tromaville. Chrissy and Lauren, two innocent lesbian lovers, must fight not only the Cretins, mutants, and monsters but also the evil Tromorganic Foodstuffs Conglomerate. Can they, and Kevin the Wonder Duck, save Tromaville High School and the world?","genre_ids":[35,27,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5493,"vote_count":178,"poster_path":"/2YC1JNgGGHrCXDT83UCpdcWLFmV.jpg","release_date":"2017-01-15","vote_average":6.458,"backdrop_path":"/u4vzkyQFGuTJ1l2SS9jZmYZG4fr.jpg","original_title":"Return to... Return to Nuke 'Em High aka Vol. 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":15969,"adult":false,"title":"The Return of Jafar","video":false,"overview":"The evil Jafar escapes from the magic lamp as an all-powerful genie, ready to plot his revenge against Aladdin. From battling elusive villains atop winged horses, to dodging flames inside an exploding lava pit, it's up to Aladdin - with Princess Jasmine and the outrageously funny Genie by his side - to save the kingdom once and for all.","genre_ids":[10751,12,16,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.6012,"vote_count":3421,"poster_path":"/7SC793qtORB6YL4mu0F5o3hfjDQ.jpg","release_date":"1994-12-15","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/mOOJm3tamy9iHg2mOEA77CM6ufZ.jpg","original_title":"The Return of Jafar","original_language":"en"},{"id":882397,"adult":false,"ti